(4085, '571ACDDA-1294-4CA5-B349-5135C7DF7994', 'Nate sent this note: Hey Dad, I''m sorry about how I have been acting recently. I was feeling really upset about what happened with mom when I got mad at you the other night and shouldn''t have taken it out on you. What Nitzan said really upset me and hurt my feelings the other night and I have been feeling sad about it over the last few days. I realize in retrospect  that she probably didn''t mean what she said or maybe I misunderstood her in the heat of the moment. I''ve just been having a really hard time with people at school and feeling lonely. Yesterday I went with mike and my other friend joe for dinner because I really needed some friends to talk to and I didn''t really have any one else i felt would be able to talk the situation through. I hope you can share some of your thoughts with me', 'David', 'Nitzan', '2017-11-01T11:41:32'),
